":"Wycliffe's Bible","description":"John Wycliffe, English theologian and professor at the University of Oxford, completed a translation of the Bible from the Latin Vulgate into Middle English. This translation is known as Wycliffe's Bible and was completed around 1382.","url":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wycliffe%27s_Bible","urlTitle":"Wikipedia - Wycliffe's Bible","jurisdictionLevel":2}],"lifeSummary":"Francis D'Oerct was born in 1360, in Shropshire, England. He had at least 1 daughter with Margaret Anna De Charlton. He died in 1436, in Shrewsbury, Shropshire, England, at the age of 76."},"et":{"1360–1436":"1360–1436","1365–1399":"1365–1399","1382–1435":"1382–1435","1436":"1436","1435":"1435","1399":"1399","1365":"1365","1360":"1360","1382":"1382","Alnwick, Northumberland, England":"Alnwick, Northumberland, England","Shropshire, England":"Shropshire, England","England":"England","Shrewsbury, Shropshire, England":"Shrewsbury, Shropshire, England"},"fi":{"1360–1436":"1360–1436","1365–1399":"1365–1399","1382–1435":"1382–1435","1436":"1436","1435":"1435","1399":"1399","1365":"1365","1360":"1360","1382":"1382","Alnwick, Northumberland, England":"Alnwick, Northumberland, England","Shropshire, England":"Shropshire, England","England":"England","Shrewsbury, Shropshire, England":"Shrewsbury, Shropshire, England"},"fr":{"1360–1436":"1360–1436","1365–1399":"1365–1399","1382–1435":"1382–1435","1436":"1436","1435":"1435","1399":"1399","1365":"1365","1360":"1360","1382":"1382","Alnwick, Northumberland, England":"Alnwick, Northumberland, Angleterre","Shropshire, England":"Shropshire, Angleterre","England":"Angleterre","Shrewsbury, Shropshire, England":"Shrewsbury, Shropshire, Angleterre","lifeSummary":"Francis D'Oerct est né en 1360, à Shropshire, Angleterre. Il a eu au moins 1 fille avec Margaret Anna De Charlton. Il est décédé en 1436, à Shrewsbury, Shropshire, Angleterre, à l’âge de 76 ans."},"de":{"1360–1436":"1360–1436","1365–1399":"1365–1399","1382–1435":"1382–1435","143